query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `competency_score_distributions` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
	`period_start` timestamp NOT NULL,
	`period_end` timestamp NOT NULL,
	`job_id` int,
	`department` varchar(100),
	`competency_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
	`total_scores` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`mean_score` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`median_score` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`std_deviation` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`bucket_0_20` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`bucket_21_40` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`bucket_41_60` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`bucket_61_80` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`bucket_81_100` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
	`trend_direction` enum('up','down','stable'),
	`trend_percentage` int,
	`calculated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
	`created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
	CONSTRAINT `competency_score_distributions_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `interviewer_agreement_tracking` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
	`application_id` int NOT NULL,
	`interview_id` int NOT NULL,
	`interviewer_ratings` text NOT NULL,
	`rating_variance` int NOT NULL,
	`agreement_score` int NOT NULL,
	`competency_agreement` text NOT NULL,
	`consensus_rating` int,
	`outlier_interviewers` text,
	`calculated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
	`created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
	CONSTRAINT `interviewer_agreement_tracking_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `email_template_versions` (
	`id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
	`template_id` int NOT NULL,
	`version_number` int NOT NULL,
	`subject` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
	`html_content` text NOT NULL,
	`text_content` text NOT NULL,
	`branding_config` text NOT NULL,
	`change_description` text,
	`created_by` int NOT NULL,
	`created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
	CONSTRAINT `email_template_versions_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
